---
title: Steak Frites with Green Beans & Roasted Garlic Butter
description: Do you consider yourself a real “meat ‘n’ potatoes” type of person? Hey, join the club!! Sure, we all claim to adore a green juice or veg-packed power bowl every now and then (see: right after we get back from the gym), but if we’re talking date night... Yeah, we got you. Introducing, this ridiculously satisfying, home-cook-friendly rendition of steak frites. Picture it: juicy, pan-seared steak, crispy oven fries, and shallot-flecked green beans, all topped with roasted garlic butter. Just don’t expect us to share, okay? We worked out this week and we’re forking hungry!
